snippet.title: Vlog Едем в Парк Lakes Park Family fun We ride a huge bicycle and a locomotive
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma with family and friends had fun at Lakes Regional Park, Fort Myers, FL. Children were playing on the playground. Then we had fun riding a huge bicycle - the whole family. It was very fun for children and family. Also we could not help riding the locomotive - the main attraction of the Lakes Park. Video for kids
